hem well. And now, with Thursday=E2=80=99s reorg, Zaz has made clear he=E2=
=80=99ll do
what=E2=80=99s necessary to reduce the sting of his declining linear TV bus=
iness and get WBD a much-desired credit-rating upgrade. And, boy, have equi=
